islike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"佳 喺度嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"我憑我自己實力留係香港 點解要去台灣 吊你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"😦😦😦"},{"pid":"e2e385c56dc5128da861f0b7c6358d18cdd3af3f","tid":2226223,"uid":83323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:53:00.000Z","msg":"佢都唔想對住香港班黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e4fbfe97aba40c8843013bf25e6ece5ba781f7","tid":2226223,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e281e576ebbf13bf9ac75f3c4fcbc512635b6414","tid":2226223,"uid":151074,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"自由身自咩首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"自首是指犯人在犯罪未被發覺前，向該管公務員（如檢察官、警察等具偵查權之人）告知其犯罪，並接受裁判。在中國大陸以及台灣，自首都是法定減刑事由之一。<br />\n<br />\n而投案是指犯罪已被發覺，但不知犯人，或已知犯人時，犯人主動到案，配合偵查並接受裁判。在台灣，投案不是法定減刑事由之一，而在中國大陸，投案是法定減刑事由之一。值得注意的是，「投案」和「自首」可能會被非法律界人士錯誤使用。<br />\n然而如果犯人犯下罪行過重（如惡性謀殺，強姦，搶劫，以及巨額貪污等），即使有自首或投案情節，有時也不會受到任何減刑。例如在中國大陸，有些主動自首或投案的犯下故意殺人罪和貪污罪的嫌犯，也會被處以死刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359eade9c43210c3e49d0e5cc77c6446dcd49e2a","tid":2226223,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"挽留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a77fbdf5a4a28419fd9a8cc18e0fd7bdce35bd","tid":2226223,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"天氣涼左，唔去自首了"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8ee258e52d4e5401767da87ffad1c7e6e3c2932d","tid":2226223,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"